{
  "info": {
    "name": "Gym SaaS API",
    "description": "Full API collection for the Gym SaaS platform.\n\n## Quick start\n1. Run the dev seed: `pnpm db:seed`\n2. Start the API: `pnpm dev` (runs on port 3001)\n3. Run **Auth → Gym Login (Staff)** — the token is auto-saved to `accessToken`\n4. All other requests use `{{accessToken}}` automatically\n\n## Dev credentials\n- Staff (MANAGER): `manager@devgym.com` / `Password123!`\n- Member: `member@devgym.com` / `Password123!`\n- Gym code: `DEVGYM`\n- Gym ID: `00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002`\n- Community Conversation ID: `00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008`\n\n## WebSocket (Chat)\nPostman supports Socket.IO natively:\n1. Click **New → Socket.IO**\n2. URL: `http://localhost:3001/chat`\n3. Under **Connection → Headers**, add: `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`\n   OR under **Connection → Auth**, add key `token` = the JWT value\n4. Connect, then emit the events documented in `docs/04-api/api-reference.md`\n\nEvents to test:\n- Emit `join` → `{\"conversationId\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008\"}`\n- Emit `message.send` → `{\"conversationId\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008\",\"content\":\"Hello!\"}`\n- Listen for `message.new` → fires for every new message in the room",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",          "value": "http://localhost:3001",                "type": "string" },
    { "key": "gymId",            "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "memberId",         "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "planId",           "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "conversationId",   "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "accessToken",      "value": "",                                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refreshToken",     "value": "",                                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "announcementId",   "value": "",                                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "messageId",        "value": "",                                     "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Resolve Code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"DEVGYM\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/resolve-code", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "resolve-code"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Gym Login (Staff — MANAGER)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "  console.log('Staff token saved.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"gymCode\": \"DEVGYM\",\n  \"email\": \"manager@devgym.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/gym/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "gym", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Gym Login (Member)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "  console.log('Member token saved.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"gymCode\": \"DEVGYM\",\n  \"email\": \"member@devgym.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/gym/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "gym", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "refresh"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "logout"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Community Chat (REST)",
      "description": "REST endpoints for chat history and actions.\n\nFor real-time messaging, use Postman's Socket.IO support:\n- New → Socket.IO → URL: http://localhost:3001/chat\n- Add auth: token = <your JWT> in handshake auth\n- Emit 'join' with { conversationId } before sending messages\n- Listen for 'message.new', 'message.deleted', 'message.reaction'\n\nSee docs/04-api/api-reference.md → WebSocket section for full event reference.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Messages (latest 50)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages?limit=50",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "messages"],
              "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "50" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Messages (load older — cursor pagination)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages?limit=50&before=2026-04-20T10:00:00.000Z",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "messages"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "50" },
                { "key": "before", "value": "2026-04-20T10:00:00.000Z", "description": "Replace with sentAt of oldest message in current batch" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Message",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('messageId', res.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"Hello community!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "messages"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Message (with reply)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"This is a reply!\",\n  \"replyToId\": \"{{messageId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "messages"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "React to Message (toggle 👍)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"emoji\": \"👍\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages/{{messageId}}/react",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "messages", "{{messageId}}", "react"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Message",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages/{{messageId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "messages", "{{messageId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mark Conversation Read",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/gyms/{{gymId}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/read",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["gyms", "{{gymId}}", "conversations", "{{conversationId}}", "read"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
